Any changes must be made mainly on the module folder. Only update root if there are schema changes (see docs/SCHEMA.md for reference).

When there are visual changes use Shadcn MCP Server

Planning Rule:

- Reuse components whenever possible
- Use whole blocks where possible (e.g., login, calendar)
- If there is a need for new component, then first call MCP demo tool to see how it is used before implementation.

Implementation Rule:

- Use docs/VISUAL_GUIDE.md
- Use docs/STACK_GUIDELINES.md